did.unittitle: Yale University Library subject card catalog

repository.corpname: Yale University. Department of Manuscripts and Archives

did.abstract: The materials consist of the Yale University Library subject catalog cards, which were retrospectively converted to electronic format.

odd.head: General note
odd.p: Forms part of Yale Record Group 32-C (YRG 32-C), Records of Yale University Library departments and offices.

acqinfo.head: Immediate Source of Acquisition
acqinfo.p: The materials were transferred from the Yale University Library, 2005.

userestrict.head: Conditions Governing Use
userestrict.p: The entire subject catalog is available via ORBIS, the Yale University Library online public access catalog (OPAC).

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Yale University Library Subject Card Catalog (RU 982). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: The materials are arranged alphabetically by subject term.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: The materials consist of the Yale University Library subject catalog cards, which were retrospectively converted to electronic format.
